# Contributing Guidelines

We welcome and actively encourage contributions to this project. Whether you want to report bugs, suggest new features, or improve the existing code.

## Steps
* Fork the project.
* Make your feature addition or bug fix.
* Ensure your code is nicely formatted in the [PSR-7](https://github.com/php-fig/fig-standards/blob/master/accepted/PSR-2-coding-style-guide.md) style.
* Send the pull request.